<P>
Why has Fox moved "Booker," one of its best shows, to the 10 p.m. time slot on 
Sundays? Doesn't it realize most of the show's fans have to get up and go to 
school Monday mornings? Fox, please ax "The Outsiders" and move "Booker" back 
to 7 p.m. "The Outsiders" is a lame excuse for a TV show anyway. 
</P>
<P>
Michelle Parkinson, Anaheim 
