FLAG BURNING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I just opened The Times to Page 2 and saw the flag-burning photograph from 
Portland, Ore., where President Bush paid a visit for a political fund raiser 
(May 22). I was angry and ashamed to see a young lady holding the flag of our 
United States while watching it burn. 
</P>
