look inthe mirror after commiting this despicable act? 
</P>
<P>
Those who deliberately burn, mutilate or walk on our "red, white and blue" 
should be punished by law. I commend our government to take action now and stop 
this unlawful act. 
</P>
<P>
DORIS B. ELLER 
