<P>
TENURED RADICALS? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Where in the world did The Times dig up this left-lib reviewer Donald Lazere? 
Cal Poly San Luis Obispo? God help us. 
</P>
<P>
JANE MALLORY 
</P>
<P>
ARCADIA 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052790-0090 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 225023 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 27, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
