</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mater Dei High's Jason Harnett and Adam Jarrett, who played doubles together 
for the first time this year only three weeks ago, won the Southern Section 
doubles title, 7-5, 7-6 (7-4), over Sean McKenna and Derek Shinden of Thousand 
Oaks on Saturday at SeaCliff Tennis Club in Huntington Beach. 
</P>
