<P>
THIRSTING FOR JUSTICE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Yes, I am doing my part in conserving water. A few years back when we went 
through this same emphasis, people in our area pitched in to do their part, 
only to be hit with a higher rate for water because we were using less. 
</P>
<P>
