Davis in "Quick Change." Robin Williams and Fran Drescher in "Cadillac Man." 
ROW 3: Steve Martin and Joan Cusack in "My Blue Heaven." Emilio Estevez in 
"Young Guns 2." Bill Cosby in "Ghost Dad." Charlie Sheen in "Navy SEAL." ROW 4: 
