HIGH SCHOOL BASEBALL SEMIFINAL PAIRINGS SET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Marina High School will meet top-seeded Westlake in the semifinals of the 
Southern Section 5-A baseball playoffs at 4 p.m. Tuesday at Blair Field in Long 
Beach. 
