AFRICA; DE KLERK, FREDERIK W; SOUTH AFRICA -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- EUROPE; 
MANDELA, NELSON R; SPEECHES; CONSERVATIVE PARTY (SOUTH AFRICA); AFRIKANERS; 
