<HEADLINE>
<P>
CAUTHEN FILLY WINS 1,000 GUINEAS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
DUBLIN, Ireland 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In The Groove, ridden by American Steve Cauthen, came out of last place to beat 
heavily favored Heart of Joy by three lengths Saturday in the Irish 1,000 
Guineas at Curragh race track. 
</P>
</TEXT>
