<TEXT>
<P>
Kenneth Kurek has been appointed president of Charter Commercial Brokerage Co. 
</P>
<P>
Kurek opened Charter's Newport Beach office in 1984 and had been regional 
manager. As president, he will be responsible for the company's four California 
offices and a Dallas office. Also, David P. Rose has been named vice 
president/regional sales manager of the Newport Beach office. Before joining 
Charter in 1986, he was with Coldwell Banker Real Estate Management. 
</P>
